  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The following contains clips from Disney's Frozen and Frozen 2.",
      "zh": "以下包含迪士尼《冰雪奇緣》和《冰雪奇緣2》的片段。",
      "ja": "以下はディズニーの『アナと雪の女王』と『アナと雪の女王2』のクリップを含みます。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now available on Blu-ray and DVD.",
      "zh": "現在可在藍光和DVD上購買。",
      "ja": "現在、ブルーレイとDVDで発売中です。",
      "time": "00:00:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Queen Elsa of Arindell.",
      "zh": "阿倫戴爾的艾莎女王。",
      "ja": "アレンデールのエルサ女王。",
      "time": "00:00:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Princess Anna of Arindell.",
      "zh": "阿倫戴爾的安娜公主。",
      "ja": "アレンデールのアナ王女。",
      "time": "00:00:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, here? Are you sure?",
      "zh": "哦，在這裡？你確定嗎？",
      "ja": "ああ、ここ？本当？",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't think I'm supposed to smell.",
      "zh": "我想我不應該聞這個。",
      "ja": "嗅いじゃいけないと思う。",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:00:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hi, me?",
      "zh": "嗨，是我嗎？",
      "ja": "こんにちは、私？",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh. Hi.",
      "zh": "哦，嗨。",
      "ja": "ああ、こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You look beautiful.",
      "zh": "你看起來很美。",
      "ja": "綺麗に見えるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:00:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You look beautiful.",
      "zh": "你看起來很美。",
      "ja": "綺麗に見えるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I mean, not fuller.",
      "zh": "我是說，不是更豐滿。",
      "ja": "つまり、ふっくらじゃなくて。",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You don't look fuller, but more beautiful.",
      "zh": "你不是看起來更豐滿，而是更美麗。",
      "ja": "ふっくらじゃなくて、もっと美しいよ。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So, this is what a party looks like.",
      "zh": "所以，這就是派對的樣子。",
      "ja": "これがパーティーってやつか。",
      "time": "00:00:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's warmer than I thought.",
      "zh": "比我想像的還溫暖。",
      "ja": "思ったより暖かいね。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What is that amazing smell?",
      "zh": "那是什麼美妙的氣味？",
      "ja": "あの素敵な匂いは何？",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Chocolate.",
      "zh": "巧克力。",
      "ja": "チョコレートだよ。",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Your Majesty.",
      "zh": "陛下。",
      "ja": "陛下。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The Duke of Weasel Tower.",
      "zh": "鼬鼠塔公爵。",
      "ja": "イタチタワー公爵。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wesselton.",
      "zh": "韋塞爾頓。",
      "ja": "ウェッセルトン。",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Duke of Wesselton.",
      "zh": "韋塞爾頓公爵。",
      "ja": "ウェッセルトン公爵。",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Your Majesty.",
      "zh": "陛下。",
      "ja": "陛下。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Has your closest partner in trade?",
      "zh": "您的最親密的貿易夥伴？",
      "ja": "あなたの最も親しい貿易相手ですか？",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It seems only fitting that I offer you your first dance's queen.",
      "zh": "我覺得很合適為您獻上第一支舞。",
      "ja": "あなたに最初のダンスを申し出るのがふさわしいようです。",
      "time": "00:01:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I took a jump.",
      "zh": "我跳了一下。",
      "ja": "ジャンプしたよ。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Only I don't dance.",
      "zh": "只是我不會跳舞。",
      "ja": "でも私は踊らないの。",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But my sister does.",
      "zh": "但我妹妹會。",
      "ja": "でも妹は踊るよ。",
      "time": "00:01:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, what?",
      "zh": "哦，什麼？",
      "ja": "ああ、何？",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lucky you.",
      "zh": "你真幸運。",
      "ja": "いいなあ。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, I don't think.",
      "zh": "哦，我不認為。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうは思わない。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If you swoon't let me know, I'll catch you.",
      "zh": "如果你暈倒了告訴我，我會接住你。",
      "ja": "もし気絶しそうなら教えて、受け止めるから。",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "zh": "抱歉。",
      "ja": "ごめんね。",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can actually pick up.",
      "zh": "我其實可以抱起來。",
      "ja": "実は抱き上げられるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm looking out.",
      "zh": "我在注意。",
      "ja": "気をつけてるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm speaking up.",
      "zh": "我在說話。",
      "ja": "声を上げてる。",
      "time": "00:01:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So great to have the gates open.",
      "zh": "大門開著真好。",
      "ja": "門が開いてて嬉しいね。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why did they shut them in the first place?",
      "zh": "他們為什麼一開始要關門？",
      "ja": "なぜ最初に閉めたんだろう？",
      "time": "00:01:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you know the reason?",
      "zh": "你知道原因嗎？",
      "ja": "理由を知ってる？",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不知道。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不知道。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hang on.",
      "zh": "等一下。",
      "ja": "ちょっと待って。",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They don't call me the little dipper for nothing.",
      "zh": "他們叫我小北斗不是沒原因的。",
      "ja": "小さなディッパーと呼ばれるのは無意味じゃないよ。",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Whoa.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "おおっと。",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I could chicken with the face of a monkey and fly.",
      "zh": "我可以像猴子臉的雞一樣飛。",
      "ja": "猿の顔をした鶏のように飛べるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I never knew winter could be so beautiful.",
      "zh": "我從不知道冬天可以這麼美麗。",
      "ja": "冬がこんなに美しいとは知らなかった。",
      "time": "00:02:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:02:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It really is beautiful, isn't it?",
      "zh": "真的很美，不是嗎？",
      "ja": "本当に美しいよね？",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's so white.",
      "zh": "好白。",
      "ja": "とても白いね。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You don't have a little color.",
      "zh": "你沒有一點顏色。",
      "ja": "少し色がないね。",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm thinking like maybe some crimson.",
      "zh": "我在想也許加點深紅色。",
      "ja": "深紅色を少し加えたらどうかな。",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Charm.",
      "zh": "魅力。",
      "ja": "魅力だね。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Choose how about yellow?",
      "zh": "選擇黃色怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "黄色はどう？",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, not yellow.",
      "zh": "不，不是黃色。",
      "ja": "いや、黄色はダメ。",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yellow and snow?",
      "zh": "黃色和雪？",
      "ja": "黄色と雪？",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, go.",
      "zh": "不，走吧。",
      "ja": "ダメ、やめて。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Am I right?",
      "zh": "我說得對嗎？",
      "ja": "私の言う通り？",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:02:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're creepy.",
      "zh": "你很怪異。",
      "ja": "気持ち悪いよ。",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Whoa.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "おっと。",
      "time": "00:02:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Back at you.",
      "zh": "你也是。",
      "ja": "そっちこそ。",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please don't talk.",
      "zh": "請不要說話。",
      "ja": "話さないで。",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You don't want to choose the hand.",
      "zh": "你不想選擇那隻手。",
      "ja": "その手は選びたくないよね。",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:02:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We got off to a bad start.",
      "zh": "我們一開始就不太好。",
      "ja": "出だしが悪かったね。",
      "time": "00:03:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll kill you with the body.",
      "zh": "我會用身體殺了你。",
      "ja": "体で殺すよ。",
      "time": "00:03:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait.",
      "zh": "等等。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:03:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What am I looking at right now?",
      "zh": "我現在在看什麼？",
      "ja": "今何を見てるの？",
      "time": "00:03:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Why are you hanging off the earth like a bat?",
      "zh": "你為什麼像蝙蝠一樣掛在地上？",
      "ja": "なぜ地面に蝙蝠のようにぶら下がってるの？",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:03:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait one second.",
      "zh": "等一下。",
      "ja": "ちょっと待って。",
      "time": "00:03:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:03:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:03:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're welcome.",
      "zh": "不客氣。",
      "ja": "どういたしまして。",
      "time": "00:03:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I'm perfect.",
      "zh": "現在我完美了。",
      "ja": "これで完璧だ。",
      "time": "00:03:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, almost.",
      "zh": "嗯，差不多。",
      "ja": "まあ、ほぼね。",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It was like my whole life got turned upside down.",
      "zh": "就像我的整個人生被顛倒了一樣。",
      "ja": "まるで人生がひっくり返ったみたいだった。",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, whoa.",
      "zh": "哦，哇。",
      "ja": "ああ、わあ。",
      "time": "00:03:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "zh": "對不起。",
      "ja": "ごめんね。",
      "time": "00:03:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "zh": "對不起。",
      "ja": "ごめん。",
      "time": "00:03:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you okay?",
      "zh": "你還好嗎？",
      "ja": "大丈夫？",
      "time": "00:03:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you kidding me?",
      "zh": "你在開玩笑嗎？",
      "ja": "冗談でしょ？",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am wonderful.",
      "zh": "我很好。",
      "ja": "私は素晴らしいよ。",
      "time": "00:03:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I've always wanted a nose.",
      "zh": "我一直想要一個鼻子。",
      "ja": "ずっと鼻が欲しかったんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's like me being a unicorn.",
      "zh": "這就像我是一隻獨角獸。",
      "ja": "まるでユニコーンみたい。",
      "time": "00:03:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, whoa.",
      "zh": "嘿，哇。",
      "ja": "ねえ、わあ。",
      "time": "00:03:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:03:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I love it even more.",
      "zh": "我更愛它了。",
      "ja": "もっと好きになったよ。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "よし。",
      "time": "00:03:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's start this thing over.",
      "zh": "讓我們重新開始。",
      "ja": "もう一度始めよう。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi, everyone.",
      "zh": "大家好。",
      "ja": "みんな、こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm all off.",
      "zh": "我是奧拉夫。",
      "ja": "僕はオラフだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I like warm hugs.",
      "zh": "我喜歡溫暖的擁抱。",
      "ja": "そして温かいハグが好きなんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All off.",
      "zh": "奧拉夫。",
      "ja": "オラフ。",
      "time": "00:03:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's right.",
      "zh": "沒錯。",
      "ja": "そうだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All off.",
      "zh": "奧拉夫。",
      "ja": "オラフ。",
      "time": "00:03:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And you.",
      "zh": "還有你。",
      "ja": "そして君。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm Anna.",
      "zh": "我是安娜。",
      "ja": "私はアナ。",
      "time": "00:03:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And who's the funky looking donkey over there?",
      "zh": "那邊那隻看起來怪怪的驢子是誰？",
      "ja": "あそこにいる変な見た目のロバは誰？",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's fun.",
      "zh": "那是斯文。",
      "ja": "それはスヴェンだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "zh": "嗯嗯。",
      "ja": "うんうん。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And who's the reindeer?",
      "zh": "那隻馴鹿是誰？",
      "ja": "あのトナカイは誰？",
      "time": "00:03:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sven.",
      "zh": "斯文。",
      "ja": "スヴェン。",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:03:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Make things easier for me.",
      "zh": "讓我更容易認識你們。",
      "ja": "わかりやすくしてくれ。",
      "time": "00:03:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, look at him trying to kiss my nose.",
      "zh": "哦，看他試圖親我的鼻子。",
      "ja": "ああ、彼が私の鼻にキスしようとしてる。",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like you too.",
      "zh": "我也喜歡你。",
      "ja": "僕も君が好きだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, love.",
      "zh": "哦，親愛的。",
      "ja": "ああ、愛しい。",
      "time": "00:03:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did Elsa build you?",
      "zh": "是艾莎造了你嗎？",
      "ja": "エルサが君を作ったの？",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's fun.",
      "zh": "那很有趣。",
      "ja": "それは楽しいね。",
      "time": "00:04:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "zh": "嗯嗯。",
      "ja": "うんうん。",
      "time": "00:04:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And who's the reindeer?",
      "zh": "那隻馴鹿是誰？",
      "ja": "あのトナカイは誰？",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sven.",
      "zh": "斯文。",
      "ja": "スヴェン。",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:04:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:04:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Make things easier for me.",
      "zh": "讓我更容易認識你們。",
      "ja": "わかりやすくしてくれ。",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:04:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like you too.",
      "zh": "我也喜歡你。",
      "ja": "僕も君が好きだよ。",
      "time": "00:04:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, love.",
      "zh": "哦，親愛的。",
      "ja": "ああ、愛しい。",
      "time": "00:04:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did Elsa build you?",
      "zh": "是艾莎造了你嗎？",
      "ja": "エルサが君を作ったの？",
      "time": "00:04:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:04:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why?",
      "zh": "為什麼？",
      "ja": "なぜ？",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you know where she is?",
      "zh": "你知道她在哪裡嗎？",
      "ja": "彼女がどこにいるか知ってる？",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "知道。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:04:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Why?",
      "zh": "為什麼？",
      "ja": "なぜ？",
      "time": "00:04:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you think you could show us the way?",
      "zh": "你覺得你能帶我們去嗎？",
      "ja": "道を案内してくれる？",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "可以。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why?",
      "zh": "為什麼？",
      "ja": "なぜ？",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How does this work?",
      "zh": "這怎麼運作？",
      "ja": "これはどうやって動くの？",
      "time": "00:04:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ow.",
      "zh": "哎呦。",
      "ja": "痛い。",
      "time": "00:04:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Stop it, Sven.",
      "zh": "別這樣，斯文。",
      "ja": "やめて、スヴェン。",
      "time": "00:04:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Trying to focus here.",
      "zh": "我在努力集中精神。",
      "ja": "集中しようとしてるんだ。",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:04:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why?",
      "zh": "為什麼？",
      "ja": "なぜ？",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They're both asleep.",
      "zh": "他們兩個都睡著了。",
      "ja": "二人とも寝てるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So what do you want to do?",
      "zh": "那你想做什麼？",
      "ja": "じゃあ、どうしたい？",
      "time": "00:04:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sven.",
      "zh": "斯文。",
      "ja": "スヴェン。",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Keep us steady, will you?",
      "zh": "幫我們穩住，好嗎？",
      "ja": "しっかり支えてくれる？",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "zh": "嗯嗯。",
      "ja": "うんうん。",
      "time": "00:04:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anna.",
      "zh": "安娜。",
      "ja": "アナ。",
      "time": "00:04:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Anna.",
      "zh": "安娜。",
      "ja": "アナ。",
      "time": "00:04:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Remember our first trip like this when I said you'd have to be crazy to want to marry a man",
      "zh": "還記得我們第一次這樣旅行時，我說你如果想嫁給一個剛認識的男人一定是瘋了",
      "ja": "こんな旅を初めてした時、君が会ったばかりの男と結婚したいなんて狂ってると言ったのを覚えてる？",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "you just met?",
      "zh": "你剛認識的？",
      "ja": "君が会ったばかりの？",
      "time": "00:04:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait, what?",
      "zh": "等等，什麼？",
      "ja": "えっ、何？",
      "time": "00:04:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Crazy?",
      "zh": "瘋了？",
      "ja": "狂ってる？",
      "time": "00:04:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You didn't say I was crazy.",
      "zh": "你沒說我是瘋子。",
      "ja": "君は僕が狂ってるとは言わなかった。",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You think I'm crazy?",
      "zh": "你覺得我瘋了嗎？",
      "ja": "僕が狂ってると思う？",
      "time": "00:04:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:04:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I did.",
      "zh": "我說了。",
      "ja": "言ったよ。",
      "time": "00:04:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You were.",
      "zh": "你是。",
      "ja": "君はそうだった。",
      "time": "00:04:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:04:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not crazy.",
      "zh": "不是瘋子。",
      "ja": "狂ってない。",
      "time": "00:04:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Clearly.",
      "zh": "很明顯。",
      "ja": "明らかに。",
      "time": "00:04:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just naive.",
      "zh": "只是天真。",
      "ja": "ただの純粋さ。",
      "time": "00:04:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Not naive.",
      "zh": "不是天真。",
      "ja": "純粋じゃない。",
      "time": "00:05:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just new to love.",
      "zh": "只是對愛情陌生。",
      "ja": "ただ恋愛に不慣れなだけ。",
      "time": "00:05:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Like I was.",
      "zh": "就像我一樣。",
      "ja": "僕もそうだった。",
      "time": "00:05:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And when you're new, you're bound to get it wrong.",
      "zh": "當你是新手時，難免會犯錯。",
      "ja": "初心者の時は間違えるのは当然だよ。",
      "time": "00:05:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So you're saying I'm wrong for you.",
      "zh": "所以你是說我不適合你。",
      "ja": "つまり、僕は君に合わないってこと？",
      "time": "00:05:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:05:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm Olaf.",
      "zh": "我是奧拉夫。",
      "ja": "僕はオラフ。",
      "time": "00:05:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, sorry.",
      "zh": "哦，抱歉。",
      "ja": "ああ、ごめん。",
      "time": "00:05:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, I just find clothes restricting.",
      "zh": "是的，我覺得衣服很束縛。",
      "ja": "うん、服は窮屈に感じるんだ。",
      "time": "00:05:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Better wondering who we are and why we're here.",
      "zh": "還不如想想我們是誰，為什麼在這裡。",
      "ja": "自分たちが誰で、なぜここにいるのか考えたほうがいいよ。",
      "time": "00:05:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's really quite simple.",
      "zh": "這真的很簡單。",
      "ja": "本当にとても簡単だよ。",
      "time": "00:05:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You begin with two sisters.",
      "zh": "故事從兩個姐妹開始。",
      "ja": "物語は二人の姉妹から始まる。",
      "time": "00:05:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "One born with magical powers.",
      "zh": "一個天生有魔法力量。",
      "ja": "一人は魔法の力を持って生まれた。",
      "time": "00:05:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One born powerless.",
      "zh": "一個天生無力。",
      "ja": "もう一人は力がない。",
      "time": "00:05:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They're love of snowmen.",
      "zh": "她們對雪人的愛。",
      "ja": "彼女たちの雪だるまへの愛。",
      "time": "00:05:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Infinite.",
      "zh": "無限。",
      "ja": "無限大だ。",
      "time": "00:05:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Anna, no, no, hey!",
      "zh": "安娜，不，不，嘿！",
      "ja": "アナ、ダメだ、ダメ、ちょっと！",
      "time": "00:05:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Glass!",
      "zh": "玻璃！",
      "ja": "ガラス！",
      "time": "00:05:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "哦！",
      "ja": "ああ！",
      "time": "00:05:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mama, Papa, help!",
      "zh": "媽媽，爸爸，救命！",
      "ja": "ママ、パパ、助けて！",
      "time": "00:05:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Slam, door shutting everywhere.",
      "zh": "砰，門到處關上了。",
      "ja": "バタン、ドアがあちこちで閉まる。",
      "time": "00:05:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sisters turn apart.",
      "zh": "姐妹分開了。",
      "ja": "姉妹は離れ離れに。",
      "time": "00:05:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, at least they have their parents.",
      "zh": "至少她們還有父母。",
      "ja": "まあ、少なくとも両親はいる。",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Their parents are dead.",
      "zh": "她們的父母已經去世了。",
      "ja": "両親は亡くなっている。",
      "time": "00:05:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, this is gonna blow!",
      "zh": "哦，這會爆炸！",
      "ja": "ああ、これは大変なことになる！",
      "time": "00:05:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Snow!",
      "zh": "雪！",
      "ja": "雪！",
      "time": "00:05:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Snow!",
      "zh": "雪！",
      "ja": "雪！",
      "time": "00:05:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Magic pulses through my snowflakes.",
      "zh": "魔法在我的雪花中脈動。",
      "ja": "魔法が僕の雪の結晶を通り抜ける。",
      "time": "00:05:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I live.",
      "zh": "我活著。",
      "ja": "僕は生きている。",
      "time": "00:05:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ice pallets for one.",
      "zh": "冰塊給一個人。",
      "ja": "一人分の氷のパレット。",
      "time": "00:05:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Ice pallets for one.",
      "zh": "冰塊給一個人。",
      "ja": "一人分の氷のパレット。",
      "time": "00:05:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Get out, Anna.",
      "zh": "出去，安娜。",
      "ja": "出て行け、アナ。",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Ooh, my heart.",
      "zh": "喔，我的心。",
      "ja": "ああ、心が。",
      "time": "00:05:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, my goodness.",
      "zh": "哦，天哪。",
      "ja": "ああ、なんてことだ。",
      "time": "00:05:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Only an act of true love can save you.",
      "zh": "只有真愛的行為能救你。",
      "ja": "真実の愛の行為だけが君を救える。",
      "time": "00:05:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here's a true love's kiss.",
      "zh": "這是一個真愛之吻。",
      "ja": "これが真実の愛のキスだ。",
      "time": "00:05:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're not worth it.",
      "zh": "你不值得。",
      "ja": "君はそれに値しない。",
      "time": "00:06:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Guess what?",
      "zh": "猜猜看？",
      "ja": "何だと思う？",
      "time": "00:06:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm the bad guy.",
      "zh": "我是壞人。",
      "ja": "僕が悪者だ。",
      "time": "00:06:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "何？",
      "time": "00:06:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "An unfreeze was to death forever.",
      "zh": "解凍就是永遠的死亡。",
      "ja": "解凍は永遠の死だ。",
      "time": "00:06:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then she unfreezes.",
      "zh": "然後她解凍了。",
      "ja": "それから彼女は解凍した。",
      "time": "00:06:11"
    },
